## Azure Functions Performance and Health overview

Provides a unified view of Azure Functions performance and reliability.
Tracks:
- Total invocations
- Top & underperforming Function Apps
- Resource utilization (memory, I/O, network)
- Error and throughput trends

Use this to identify scaling patterns, performance bottlenecks, and reliability issues.
